  GHC-Options:          -Wall
  GHC-Prof-Options:     -auto-all -caf-all -rtsopts
  Exposed-Modules:      System.Posix.Pty
  Other-Modules:        

  C-Sources:            cbits/fork_exec_with_pty.c cbits/pty_size.c
  CC-Options:           -Wall -Wextra -pedantic -std=c99
